SELECT COALESCE("USERID", "USERID") AS "USERID", "DISPLAYNAME", "TOTALBADGES", "TOTALPOSTS", "TOTALQUESTIONS", "TOTALANSWERS", "TOTALTAGWIKIS", "POSITIVEPOSTS", "CONTRIBUTORSTATUS"
FROM (SELECT "Users"."Id" AS "USERID", "Users"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", CASE WHEN "t1"."TOTALBADGES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t1"."TOTALBADGES" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALBADGES", CASE WHEN "t3"."TOTALPOSTS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."TOTALPOSTS" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALPOSTS", CASE WHEN "t3"."TOTALQUESTIONS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."TOTALQUESTIONS" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALQUESTIONS", CASE WHEN "t3"."TOTALANSWERS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."TOTALANSWERS" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALANSWERS", CASE WHEN "t3"."TOTALTAGWIKIS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."TOTALTAGWIKIS" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALTAGWIKIS", CASE WHEN "t3"."POSITIVEPOSTS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."POSITIVEPOSTS" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "POSITIVEPOSTS", CASE WHEN CASE WHEN "t1"."TOTALBADGES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t1"."TOTALBADGES" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END > 10 THEN 'Active Contributor' WHEN CASE WHEN "t3"."TOTALPOSTS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."TOTALPOSTS" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END > 100 THEN 'Veteran           ' ELSE 'New Contributor   ' END AS "CONTRIBUTORSTATUS"
FROM "STACK"."Users"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT ANY_VALUE("Users0"."Id") AS "USERID", "Users0"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", COUNT("Badges"."Id") AS "TOTALBADGES", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "GOLDBADGES", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "SILVERBADGES", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "BRONZEBADGES"
FROM "STACK"."Users" AS "Users0"
LEFT JOIN "STACK"."Badges" ON "Users0"."Id" = "Badges"."UserId"
GROUP BY "Users0"."Id", "Users0"."DisplayName") AS "t1" ON "Users"."Id" = "t1"."USERID"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "OwnerUserId" AS "OWNERUSERID", COUNT(*) AS "TOTALPOSTS", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "TOTALQUESTIONS", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "TOTALANSWERS", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 4 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "TOTALTAGWIKIS", SUM(CASE WHEN "Score" > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "POSITIVEPOSTS"
FROM "STACK"."Posts"
GROUP BY "OwnerUserId") AS "t3" ON "Users"."Id" = "t3"."OWNERUSERID") AS "t4"
WHERE "t4"."TOTALPOSTS" > 0